00:19:21.800 --> 00:19:23.800
So drag as a force.

00:19:23.800 --> 00:19:32.990
So this is just newtons or mass,
length per time squared.

00:19:32.990 --> 00:19:34.820
Does that help?

00:19:34.820 --> 00:19:39.250
So it's just newtons,
in SI units.

00:19:39.250 --> 00:19:42.230
Or in general, mass length per
time squared, so a mass times

00:19:42.230 --> 00:19:43.480
an acceleration.

00:19:46.980 --> 00:19:51.970
So now, we've matched
the units of mass.

00:19:51.970 --> 00:19:54.170
But we haven't matched the
units of time yet.

