00:19:56.610 --> 00:19:58.140
There's no time there.

00:19:58.140 --> 00:20:00.940
There's t to the
minus 2 there.

00:20:00.940 --> 00:20:03.890
Well, what can we
do about that?

00:20:06.950 --> 00:20:11.080
