00:20:11.080 --> 00:20:12.960
And the problem is we
don't know how much.

00:20:12.960 --> 00:20:16.640
So the time doesn't
help us enough.

00:20:16.640 --> 00:20:20.900
Turns out to make the time
and the length work, the

00:20:20.900 --> 00:20:27.020
simultaneous constraint, the
only way to do it is that.

00:20:27.020 --> 00:20:30.580
You make the same argument to
get the masses to match, the

00:20:30.580 --> 00:20:32.450
lengths to match, and
the times to match.

00:20:32.450 --> 00:20:33.840
This is the only way to do it.

00:20:33.840 --> 00:20:35.790
So you don't have
any viscosity.

00:20:35.790 --> 00:20:38.880
So actually, that's the simplest
experiment I know to

00:20:38.880 --> 00:20:41.350
show that the drag
at high speed--

00:20:41.350 --> 00:20:43.390
in other words, most flows are
actually high speed, high

00:20:43.390 --> 00:20:47.670
Reynolds number-- is independent
of viscosity.

00:20:47.670 --> 00:20:51.510
So it's rho av squared.

00:20:51.510 --> 00:20:55.530
And that is a great result,
because it tells you all kinds

00:20:55.530 --> 00:20:58.290
of stuff about everyday flows
in everyday life.

00:20:58.290 --> 00:21:01.630
Like for example, why did people
reduce the speed limit

00:21:01.630 --> 00:21:05.000
on the highway back in the
'70s to preserve gas?

00:21:05.000 --> 00:21:08.450
Well, on the highway,
you're burning

00:21:08.450 --> 00:21:11.140
gasoline to fight drag.

00:21:11.140 --> 00:21:13.740
So if you reduce the speed,
you reduce the drag, you

00:21:13.740 --> 00:21:15.050
reduce the amount of gasoline.

00:21:15.050 --> 00:21:18.330
So in particular, if you reduce
the speed by 20%, you

00:21:18.330 --> 00:21:22.385
reduce v squared by 40%, which
reduces the drag by 40%.

00:21:22.385 --> 00:21:26.260
So you just decreased the gas
consumption by about 40%.

00:21:26.260 --> 00:21:28.270
So you can see all these things
right away just from

00:21:28.270 --> 00:21:31.280
this simple formula, which is
a immediate consequence of

00:21:31.280 --> 00:21:34.430
this experiment.

00:21:34.430 --> 00:21:36.670
Now, it turns out this--

00:21:36.670 --> 00:21:37.940
