Then what do you actually
do when you

00:59:19.900 --> 00:59:20.960
come into the classroom?

00:59:20.960 --> 00:59:22.500
Lecture planning and
performing--

00:59:22.500 --> 00:59:24.080
how do you plan one lecture?

00:59:24.080 --> 00:59:27.630
So this is the overall structure
of the whole course.

00:59:27.630 --> 00:59:29.510
How do you plan and perform
one lecture?

