Topic eight is teaching with
blackboards and slides.

00:59:49.080 --> 00:59:52.130
So what are the advantages,
generally speaking, of

00:59:52.130 --> 00:59:52.880
blackboards?

00:59:52.880 --> 00:59:56.650
But what are situations where
slides are actually a really

00:59:56.650 --> 00:59:59.840
helpful way to teach?

00:59:59.840 --> 01:00:02.330
Slides meaning-- well,
it could be old-style

01:00:02.330 --> 01:00:07.170
photographic slides, but
